Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 05.02.2024

Welcome to Inventor's Crafting Laboratory! This Privacy Policy describes our policies and procedures regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your information when you use the Inventor's Crafting Laboratory Game. It also informs you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.

We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a transparent approach to data handling.

1. Data Collection

Inventor's Crafting Laboratory collects minimal data to ensure the proper functioning of the game. The data collected includes your PlayStore account name, which is used for game progress synchronization and to provide a personalized gaming experience. No other personal data is collected from our users.

2. Information Use and Disclosure

The information collected (PlayStore account name) is solely used for in-game functionality and is not shared with any third parties, except as necessary for the functioning of the game (e.g., cloud synchronization of game progress).

3. Ads in Game

Inventor's Crafting Laboratory may contain ads provided by third-party ad networks. These ad networks may use their own sets of information, but they do not have access to personal data from our game, as we collect minimal data. We encourage users to review the privacy policies of these third-party ad networks for more information.

4. Support & Bug Reports

For any queries or issues regarding Inventor's Crafting Laboratory, please feel free to contact us:

On our Discord server: https://discord.gg/wB8fP32ZbD
Via email at: brodoandcostudio@gmail.com
5. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Changes are effective when they are posted on this page.

6. Your Consent to This Privacy Policy

By playing Inventor's Crafting Laboratory, you signify your acceptance of this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please refrain from using our game.

7. Contact Us

For any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

Via our Discord: https://discord.gg/wB8fP32ZbD
By email: brodoandcostudio@gmail.com
Thank you for playing Inventor's Crafting Laboratory!
